Abia State government has inaugurated an inter-ministerial Task Force of the Ministries of Transport and Trade/Investments to sanitise  Osisioma Flyover and interchange as well as rid them of street trading, illegal motor parks and touting.
 
The Task Force is to oversee the maintenance of order within Flyovers and their environs, and return them to a status befitting  Aba, the commercial city of Abia. 